---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our Process — Meridian" description="See exactly what happens every day inside the Meridian SEO pipeline. Daily audits, content intelligence, performance reporting.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-dark to-dark-card pt-32 pb-20 md:pb-28">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent mb-6">The Meridian Pipeline</p>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-hero-text leading-[1.05] tracking-tight max-w-4xl">
        SEO infrastructure that runs every day.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-body-muted max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        Here's exactly what happens behind the scenes — no vague 'strategy sessions', no waiting for the monthly report.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Timeline -->
  <section class="py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6">
      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Vertical line -->
        <div class="absolute left-6 md:left-8 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-gray-200"></div>

        <!-- Monday — Content Intelligence -->
        <div class="relative pl-16 md:pl-20 pb-16">
          <div class="absolute left-0 w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/10">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.348 14.651a3.75 3.75 0 010-5.303m5.304 0a3.75 3.75 0 010 5.303m-7.425 2.122a6.75 6.75 0 010-9.546m9.546 0a6.75 6.75 0 010 9.546M5.106 18.894c-3.808-3.808-3.808-9.98 0-13.789m13.788 0c3.808 3.808 3.808 9.981 0 13.79M12 12h.008v.007H12V12zm.375 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-accent mb-2">Monday Morning</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Content Intelligence</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">Every week we scan Google News, Reddit, HackerNews, and industry publications to identify trending topics relevant to your business. This intelligence feeds into every content decision for the week.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Every Weekday — Technical Audit -->
        <div class="relative pl-16 md:pl-20 pb-16">
          <div class="absolute left-0 w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/10">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 21l-5.197-5.197m0 0A7.5 7.5 0 105.196 5.196a7.5 7.5 0 0010.607 10.607z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-accent mb-2">Every Weekday</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Technical Audit</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">Each morning we pull fresh data from Google Search Console and our rank tracker, then fetch your actual live pages to check title tags, meta descriptions, H1s, canonical tags, and indexability. We're looking for rank drops, CTR opportunities, and technical issues — with the exact current values, not guesses.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Every Weekday — Content Production -->
        <div class="relative pl-16 md:pl-20 pb-16">
          <div class="absolute left-0 w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/10">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.862 4.487l1.687-1.688a1.875 1.875 0 112.652 2.652L10.582 16.07a4.5 4.5 0 01-1.897 1.13L6 18l.8-2.685a4.5 4.5 0 011.13-1.897l8.932-8.931zm0 0L19.5 7.125M18 14v4.75A2.25 2.25 0 0115.75 21H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 013 18.75V8.25A2.25 2.25 0 015.25 6H10" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-accent mb-2">Every Weekday</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Content Production</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">Our content system checks what already exists before creating anything new. Drafts are written against your brand voice and keyword strategy — and every page with an existing draft is skipped so we never recreate work.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Every Weekday — Daily Briefing -->
        <div class="relative pl-16 md:pl-20 pb-16">
          <div class="absolute left-0 w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/10">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14.857 17.082a23.848 23.848 0 005.454-1.31A8.967 8.967 0 0118 9.75v-.7V9A6 6 0 006 9v.75a8.967 8.967 0 01-2.312 6.022c1.733.64 3.56 1.085 5.455 1.31m5.714 0a24.255 24.255 0 01-5.714 0m5.714 0a3 3 0 11-5.714 0" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-accent mb-2">Every Weekday</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Daily Briefing</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">A concise summary lands in your inbox: what changed, what's ready to publish, and the single highest-impact action you can take today.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Every Friday — Weekly Report -->
        <div class="relative pl-16 md:pl-20 pb-16">
          <div class="absolute left-0 w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/10">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875v-6.75zM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V8.625zM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V4.125z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-accent mb-2">Every Friday</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Weekly Report + Client Email</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">A full performance report (clicks, impressions, CTR, position — week over week) plus a ready-to-send client email with percentage changes only. No raw numbers that require explanation.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Monthly — Strategy Review -->
        <div class="relative pl-16 md:pl-20">
          <div class="absolute left-0 w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/10">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 6.75V15m6-6v8.25m.503 3.498l4.875-2.437c.381-.19.622-.58.622-1.006V4.82c0-.836-.88-1.38-1.628-1.006l-3.869 1.934c-.317.159-.69.159-1.006 0L9.503 3.252a1.125 1.125 0 00-1.006 0L3.622 5.689C3.24 5.88 3 6.27 3 6.695V19.18c0 .836.88 1.38 1.628 1.006l3.869-1.934c.317-.159.69-.159 1.006 0l4.994 2.497c.317.158.69.158 1.006 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-accent mb-2">Monthly</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Strategy Review</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">A month-over-month analysis deck covering what moved, what didn't, competitive signals, and next month's priorities. This is where bespoke strategy lives.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bespoke Layer -->
  <section class="bg-dark py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-[44px] font-semibold text-hero-text leading-tight">The system is standard. The strategy isn't.</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-body-muted text-lg leading-relaxed">Every client has different keywords, different competitors, different content voices, and different technical footprints. The pipeline is the same. What it finds and what it creates is entirely yours.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-16 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
        <div class="border border-dark-border rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-hero-text mb-2">Custom keyword strategy</h3>
          <p class="text-body-muted leading-relaxed text-[15px]">Keyword strategy built from scratch for your business.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-dark-border rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-hero-text mb-2">Your brand voice</h3>
          <p class="text-body-muted leading-relaxed text-[15px]">Brand voice guidelines that govern every piece of content.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-dark-border rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-hero-text mb-2">Competitor intelligence</h3>
          <p class="text-body-muted leading-relaxed text-[15px]">Competitor analysis specific to your market.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-dark to-dark-card py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-[44px] font-semibold text-hero-text leading-tight">Ready to see the pipeline in action?</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-body-muted text-lg">We'll walk you through what a week looks like for your business.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="mt-10 inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-accent hover:bg-accent-hover text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">
        Book an intro call
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
